{"tid":2192442,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚] 關於封鎖功能嘅改善建議","createTime":"2020-09-07T06:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T18:05:44.000Z","uid":161684,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"72101cc70ac2a88de6e1986a45943c363c72514d","tid":2192442,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:27:13.000Z","msg":"眾所周知連登作為香港龍頭討論區係一大滲透目標<br />\n用戶受五毛公關公司打手困擾<br />\n因此封鎖功能相當重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但好多時候用戶想要嘅其實唔係完全封鎖<br />\n而係希望透過封鎖功能做到一種起底同警示嘅作用<br />\n以下有幾點建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">1</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6Px8BQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6Px8BQ.png&h=3a20fdb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放寬封鎖原因字數限制（現為30字）<br />\n並將原因預設為該回覆嘅連結 再容許用戶修改<br />\n總之以某種方式令用戶及後可以快捷查閱封鎖特定用戶嘅緣起<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">2</span></span></strong><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jMoV6ow.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjMoV6ow.png&h=0607d83c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由回覆可以直接駁去封鎖名單<br />\n查閱已封鎖用戶當初嘅封鎖原因<br />\n可以免得要離開當前主題頁<br />\n<br />\n拋咗個磚先 暫時係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cbafc08c882ae86c86d2c87a987c358e519652","tid":2192442,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:38:06.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a82f0bcda1fec0e305196ec5765dae97553628","tid":2192442,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:54:52.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30533104f39c0c35949012be306ff5bc3ef81a00","tid":2192442,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:24:1